text: The following lists events that have happened in 1808 in the Sublime State of Persia. ==Incumbents== * Monarch: Fat′h-Ali Shah Qajar ==Birth== * January 5 – Mohammad Shah Qajar, third king of Qajar Dynasty, was born in Tabriz, Iran. ==References== Persia Category:Years of the 19th century in Iran Category:1800s in Iran Persia
